707456f-c.title: Brooklyn: Wyckoff Ave. - Weirfield St.
707456f-c.text:
Wyckoff Ave., at the S.W. corner of Weirfield Street, showing the
Laibach and Ehnis' Brewery in a set of three views. It still stands in
1929. The trolley tracks are on Wyckoff Ave.
1922.
View 2:eAugust 1923.
View 3:eApril 1923.
